and onsite labor solutions the company accepts various types of electronics for recycling such as computers computer boards cr as of april   waste management  recycling products inc was acquired by colt refining inc waste management  recycling products inc provides electronics recycling solutions its services include electronics recycling removalpickup asset recovery equipment buyouts and purchases physical and data destruction warehousingstorage evaluations and consultations appraisal refurbishing and reuse and inventory services and detailed reporting as well as disassembly demanufacturing and destruction services and transportation logistics packaging and onsite labor solutions the company accepts various types of electronics for recycling such as computers computer boards crts hard drives modems computer accessories and components cables and printers office electronics and equipment medical equipment and telephones systems and communications equipment it also resells used and surplus computer systems and electronics including laptops hard drives wireless laptop cards lcd monitors and surge protectors for power and telephone and spy sweeper a tool for detecting removing and blocking spyware the company was incorporated in  and is based in schenectady new york detailed description scotia glenville industrial park roadc streetbuilding scotia ny united statesfounded in  phone  fax  key executives for waste management  recycling products inc waste management  recycling products inc does not have any key executives recorded similar private companies by industry company name region  energy fund inc united states  class corp united states  solution corp united states  junkusa united states  pablo inc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions available in the past  months request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global blo