ste containment bulk liquid nuclear waste containment  products found products by pactec inc spill containment bermpac  spill berms pactec offers several portable spill containment solutions we call them bermpacs® the singlepiece heatwelded bermpacs® provide a safe easy and costeffective solution for secondary spill containment aimed at helping you prevent costly incidents common sizes range from ’ to ’ but pactec can manufacture any custom size needed bermpacs® are offered in a variety of materials that are uv and chemical resistant flexible bermpac  collapsible spill tray this collapsible compact and portable spill tray is small enough to fit behind the seat of your vehicle when rolled and strapped it sets up in seconds is available in multiple sizes and is made of lightweight and durable chemical resistant materials pactec’s collapsible bermpac® performs the same duty of catching and holding spilled liquids as a traditional berm but in a compact form and taking mere seconds to set up transpac  transformer containment bags pactec’s transpac transformer containment bag is the safe way to contain leaking transformers for transport to service centers our proprietary design is the first in the industry to utilize a zipper closure for ease of use in the field the heavyduty multilayer bag includes a full absorbent inner layer and is also lightweight compact and easily stored on service trucks dewatering filtration depac  dewatering filters our disposable multilayered dewatering liner works seamlessly with your waste containers to provide a cost effective solution for dewatering sludges and capturing solids for disposal or recovery the depac® utilizes gravity along with screen and nonwoven layers to thoroughly dewater your waste stream geopac  geotextile dewatering tubes the geopac is a geotextile tube used for dewatering and volume reduction of various types of sludge material the geopac® uses internal pressure to dewater instead of relying solely on gravity this allows you to dewater large volumes of sludge more efficiently than typical dewatering boxes saving you time and money waste packaging railpac  railcar liners and tarps railpac ensures the safe transport of contaminated waste materials with a formfit design to keep the liner securely in place manufactured from a choice of extruded or woven polymeric fabrics these liners and tarps are designed to exact railcar specifications as well as custom sizes the patented zipper closure ensures easy installation and can be fitted with a tamper indication device to deter unauthorized access liftpac  selfstanding un rated bulk bag pactec’s liftpac® is the only self standing zippertop hazardous waste bag on the market this cubic yard bag is the perfect solution for disposal of household hazardous waste contaminated ppe and a variety of other applications the liftpac® walls are constructed of rigid corrugated fiberboard allowing the bag to be selfstanding while the glued in  mil pe liner provides ultimate leak protection it contains the equivalent of four transliner  formfit disposable container liners the transliner® is a disposable polyethylene container liner with a revolutionary design that ensures a form fit every time our design positions the liner seals outside of the container providing exceptional leak protection to safely and securely transport solids and sludge wastes the transliner® may also be fitted to cover the load which aids in dust and odor control waste containment landpac  landfill covers the landpac can help you realize tremendous savings perfect for use with autocovering systems or oldfashioned manpower the landpac can be designed to withstand high wind conditions by including extras such as fasteners and weighted pockets our alternate daily landfill cover is manufactured using fireretardant woven polymeric materials it prevents water infiltration and aids in debris and odor control transcover  tarpaulins trap cover the transcover  is a custom manufactured tarp utilizing quality high strength yet lightweight fabrics many standard sizes are stocked to provide quick turnaround from waterproof to mesh to a full line of bungee accessories pactec has your tarp needs covered bulk liquid pactank  multi layered bulk liquid package the pactank is a multilayered bulk liquid package the pactank allows users to take advantage of readily available sealand intermodal or b containers and convert them to bulk liquid containers a key feature is the patentpending outer strapping system that reduces the energy exerted on the container therefore reducing wave action and ensuring safe transportation nuclear waste containment liftpac  model ip  certified lift bag liftpac is a dotcertified ipip flexible container for flowable solids manufactured from heavyduty woven and nonwoven polypropylene with patented zipper closures the product gives users a safe and secure way to store transport and dispose of wastes such as sand soil and gravel and construction debris liftpacs can be easily transported by rail flatbed dump truck intermodal container and barge contact supplier contact supplier your message your email your first name your last name i would like to receive periodic email updates and special offers from select suppliers yes please match my request to similar suppliers using xprt sourcing send message cancel and close by continuing you agree to the terms  conditions and privacy policy of this website waste management  recycling products inc  scotia ny waste management  recycling products inc waste management  c street scotia ny  •   website waste profile directions contact request pricing waste management is a leading provider of comprehensive environmental solutions services in north america serving more than  million customers in the us and canada as part of our strategy we are committed to developing new waste solutions that can help communities and organizations achieve their green goals including zero waste acceptable materials inorganic liq